# Placeholder A-Box.
#
# This file is the only tracked entry under ontology/dump/; the rest of the
# directory is gitignored. It exists so Fuseki's assembler (which loads this
# path via ja:externalContent in ontology/fuseki/configuration/uaf.ttl) can
# satisfy its hard file-existence check on a fresh clone, before any MSOSA
# export or dump_to_rdf.py run has populated real instance data.
#
# `python ontology/codegen/dump_to_rdf.py` overwrites this file with the live
# A-Box dumped from Neo4j; that path is the source of truth at runtime.
# Do not add hand-written triples here — they will be silently overwritten.

@prefix uafinst: <http://msosa-toolbox.local/uaf/instance#> .
